# 统一换行符：仓库内一律存 LF，避免 Windows 的 core.autocrlf 造成整文件级伪差异
* text=auto eol=lf

# 明确按二进制处理，杜绝被当成文本而损坏
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.avif binary
*.webp binary
*.pdf binary
*.zip binary
*.rar binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
*.ttf binary
*.eot binary
*.mp3 binary
*.mp4 binary
